    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\t\t\t   Mine - Taylor Swift\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By : Dylan Eurich\r\ne-mail: Dyl.eurich@gmail.com\r\n\r\nTuning: EADG\r\n\r\nListen to the song with headphones in so you can hear how the bass goes,\r\nit is a little soft, but most of this should be right. its all in the song.\r\n\r\nNo Bass Until 0.34 seconds, or the Pre-chorus to be exact\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus (x3)            Play this at the end of 3rd time\r\nG|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5~----------|---9h10-9----------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--3~/---5~--------|----------10-10----5~----------------------------------|\r\nE|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus (x2)                                 Play this after 2nd time\r\nG|-----------------------------------------|--------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|---------10-10-10-10------------|\r\nA|--33333333----------55555555----7-7--5-5-|--3~-3~-------------------------|\r\nE|-----------33333333----------------------|----------------------8-8-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse - come in at flash forward\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----5~---------------------------------5~--------------------------------|\r\nA|--------5~----7-7---3~-----5---05---3~------5~---7-7---3~------5~---------|\r\nE|----------------------3-3---------------------------------3-3-------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus         \r\nG|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5~-----------------5~----------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--3~/---5~--0-5-0-5-0-3~/---375~-0-5-0-5-0-3~----5~----------------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------------------------3~------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus Cont.\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------9-9h10p9----------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--10-12----------10-10-9-7-5----------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus (x2)                                 \r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--33333333----------55555555----7-7--5-5----------------------------------|\r\nE|-----------33333333-------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------555-0-5--------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--33333330---------0-5-0-55555555---7-7--5-5------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Post - Chorus (x2)\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----3~-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--3~-----3h5--------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------7h9p7--------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---7~----3~----5~-------9--7~----3~-------5~------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus (x3)            Play this at the end of 3rd time\r\nG|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5~----------|---9h10-9----------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--3~/---5~--------|----------10-12-10-5-3~--------------------------------|\r\nE|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus - First time no bass\r\nG|-----------------0-3-0-55555-3--------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------55555---------------5-3----------------------------------------|\r\nA|--33333333--------------------------555555/0------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](x2)\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--33333333----------55555555-7-7--5-5-------------------------------------|\r\nE|-----------33333333-------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--33333333-----------5555555555555555-------------------------------------|\r\nE|-----------33333333-------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](this part might be a little off, i couldnt get it exactly\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5~-0-5---------------------5~-0-5----9h10p9-------------------------|\r\nA|--333-------5~-555--7775--3---333--------5~--------10-9-------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5~-0-5------7-9-10--9h10p9------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--333--------5~------------------10-12-10-9-5~----------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
